"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">This can be trap,creature, or npc. Or any combination of them one per line. this is used to pick which Type the template will show up under. And defaults to all of them.</p>\n"
