"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">The following lines are regular spells. Use &lt; to start blerbs of description and &gt; to end them. use %s to add a spell save DC to the spell. Use dice notation freely inbetween &lt; &gt; without fear of them being changed.</p>\n"
